OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some patchy
OL,6,Frain, this mostly across Argyll.
OL,7,FOtherwise a dry day with some bright
OL,8,Fspells breaking through by afternoon.
OL,9,Falthough Argyll likely to stay cloudy.
OL,10,FMilder than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry. The
OL,13,Frest of the night will be mainly dry
OL,14,Falthough rather cloudy, perhaps a
OL,15,Flittle rain developing across Argyll
OL,16,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
