OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,6,Fspreading to Argyll in the morning,
OL,7,Fthen remaining areas in the afternoon.
OL,8,FA mild morning but becoming somewhat
OL,9,Fcolder in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Ffor most of Thursday but rain likely
OL,13,Fby evening. Unsettled with showers or
OL,14,Flonger spells of rain on Friday and
OL,15,FSaturday.
